The NHS is at the end of a challenging winter period. Staff face similar pressures to last year, with ambulances queuing outside hospitals and people waiting in A&E or for routine operations.
Enter a postcode to find out what is happening in your area with A&E, ambulances and hospital waiting lists across the UK.
